
extends template.pug

block content
  .container
    img(src="M5_logo.png" alt="Timestamp Logo")
  .container
    h2 API Project: File Analyser - Express
    h3 User Stories:
    ol
      li I can submit a Form object that includes a file upload.
      li When I submit something, I will receive the file infos within the JSON response.

    - action = apilink

    h3 Upload a File
    form(action=action enctype="multipart/form-data" method="POST")
      input(type="hidden" name="MAX_FILE_SIZE" value="102400")
      label(for="input_1") Select a file:
      input#input_1(type="file" name="upfile")
      input(type="submit" value="Upload")

    h3 Example Output:
    p: code { "name": "example.txt", "type": "text/plain", "size": "1284" }
